<SYNC Start=1590226><P Class=KRCC>그래요
<SYNC Start=1591303><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1595308><P Class=KRCC>함께 들어가지 않을래요
<SYNC Start=1598915><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
